                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;While working on flex scoring branch and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3012&quot; title=&quot;if you use setNorm, lucene writes a headerless separate norms file&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-3012&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I noticed it was difficult to navigate &lt;br/&gt;
